---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Cloud Business Phone System | VoIP & PBX Solutions – My Call Connect" description="Empower your business with My Call Connect’s cloud-based phone system. Scalable, reliable, and integrated with CRM for seamless communication.">
  <fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json">
      {
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "My Call Connect",
        "url": "https://www.mycallconnect.com",
        "logo": "https://www.mycallconnect.com/images/mycalllogo.png",
        "description": "Premium cloud-based business phone system and VoIP solutions.",
        "contactPoint": {
          "@type": "ContactPoint",
          "telephone": "+1-555-0123",
          "contactType": "customer service"
        }
      }
      </script>
      <script type="application/ld+json">
      {
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "FAQPage",
        "mainEntity": [{
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "How scalable is the cloud system?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Our cloud structure empowers infinite scalability. Whether you have 5 agents or 5,000, you can provision new numbers, lines, and accounts instantly through the web dashboard—without needing to modify any hardware on your end."
          }
        }, {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Does My Call Connect provide international DIDs?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Yes, we provide Direct Inward Dialing (DID) numbers across more than 50 countries and all 50 US states. You can establish a local presence nearly anywhere in the world in just a few clicks."
          }
        }, {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "What is the average latency for international calls?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "By utilizing our proprietary global edge network and optimized SIP trunking, our international latency is consistently under 150ms round-trip, resulting in completely imperceptible delays and zero-clipping audio quality."
          }
        }, {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Can I integrate this with our current CRM?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Absolutely. My Call Connect operates with an API-first methodology, offering seamless webhook and REST integrations into Salesforce, HubSpot, Zendesk, and over 100+ platforms effortlessly."
          }
        }]
      }
      </script>
  </fragment>

  <section id="home" class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-ring ring-1 hide-on-mobile"></div>
      <div class="hero-ring ring-2 hide-on-mobile"></div>

      <div class="ui-chip chip-1">
        <div class="chip-icon">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"></polygon>
          </svg>
        </div>
        Zero Latency
      </div>
      <div class="ui-chip chip-2">
        <div class="chip-icon">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path
              d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z">
            </path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        Active Call
      </div>
      <div class="ui-chip chip-3">
        <div class="chip-icon">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        Global Ping
      </div>

      <div class="hero-content animate-up">
        <span class="badge">Next-Gen Infrastructure</span>
        <h1>Cloud Business Phone System <br><span class="text-gradient">for Modern Enterprises</span></h1>
        <p class="delay-1 animate-up">Break free from legacy systems. Our cloud architecture delivers zero-latency
          routing, infinite scalability, and an interface that empowers your global team instantly.</p>
        <div class="hero-cta delay-2 animate-up">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line>
              <polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline>
            </svg></a>
          <a href="/solutions" class="text-link">Explore VoIP Solutions</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Why <span class="text-gradient-primary">Choose Our VoIP Solutions</span></h2>
        <p>Experience the ultimate calling infrastructure that empowers your team and delights your clients.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-4">
        <div class="card card-hover-effect">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <polygon points="12 2 2 7 12 12 22 7 12 2"></polygon>
              <polyline points="2 17 12 22 22 17"></polyline>
              <polyline points="2 12 12 17 22 12"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Perfect Solution</h3>
          <p>SIP Trunking connects your on-premises phone system to the PSTN over an IP network, enabling flawless voice
            calls globally.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card card-hover-effect">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
              <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Always On Time</h3>
          <p>Zero latency, instantaneous routing. We deliver reliable communication solutions to keep your operations
            running smoothly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card card-hover-effect">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"></polygon>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Hard Working</h3>
          <p>Dedicated infrastructure and relentless commitment to providing top-tier services to fuel your business
            success.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card card-hover-effect">
          <div class="card-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>24/7 Availability</h3>
          <p>Uninterrupted support. We are available around the clock to ensure your communications never drop.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid-2">
        <div>
          <h2 class="section-title">What is <span class="text-gradient-primary">Call Center Software?</span></h2>
          <p class="section-desc">A digital platform that forms the bridge between businesses and clients. Modern
            contact center software automates queries and intelligently routes them in the cloud.</p>
          <p class="section-desc">Clients today demand multi-channel communication: voice, text, chat, and social media.
            Only advanced contact centers can provide this unified experience, elevating your brand's image whether you
            have one agent or thousands.</p>
          <div class="deployment-types">
            <h3>Types of Deployments</h3>
            <div class="deploy-card deploy-onprem">
              <h4>On-Premise Software</h4>
              <p>Conventional setups relying on internal hardware. Your IT handles implementation, maintenance, and
                complex upgrades.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="deploy-card deploy-cloud">
              <span class="badge-cloud">RECOMMENDED</span>
              <h4>Cloud-Based Software</h4>
              <p>Hosted in world-class data centers. Agents connect from anywhere. Zero infrastructure maintenance,
                infinite scalability.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="content-image">
          <div class="content-icon">
            <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M21 2v6h-6"></path>
              <path d="M21 13a9 9 0 1 1-3-7.7L21 8"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Infinite Scalability</h3>
          <p>Transition from legacy systems to a unified, modern interface in minutes.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>The Right Choice for <br><span class="text-gradient-primary">Your Calling Needs</span></h2>
        <p>Specialized tools designed to simplify operations, skyrocket efficiency, and empower your agents to serve
          clients brilliantly.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-2">
        <div class="feature-list">
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-item-num">01</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Enhanced Control</h3>
              <p>Cloud-based architecture unlocks powerful features like advanced call forwarding, smart routing, and
                seamless conferencing.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-item-num">02</div>
            <div>
              <h3>User-Friendliness</h3>
              <p>An intuitive, blazing-fast dashboard. All functions managed from a single pane of glass—zero technical
                training required.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-list">
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-item-num">03</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Highly Scalable</h3>
              <p>Grow without limits. Add users, numbers, and premium features instantly without infrastructural
                modifications.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div class="feature-item-num">04</div>
            <div>
              <h3>Cost-Effectiveness</h3>
              <p>Eliminate expensive PBX hardware. No massive upfront investments, no maintenance fees—just a
                predictable, affordable service.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="faq">
    <div class="container container-sm">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Frequently Asked <span class="text-gradient-primary">Questions</span></h2>
        <p>Everything you need to know about the product and billing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question">How scalable is the cloud system? <div class="faq-icon"><svg width="24" height="24"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
              </svg></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">Our cloud structure empowers infinite scalability. Whether you have 5 agents or 5,000,
            you can provision new numbers, lines, and accounts instantly through the web dashboard—without needing to
            modify any hardware on your end.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question">Does My Call Connect provide international DIDs? <div class="faq-icon"><svg
                width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
              </svg></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">Yes, we provide Direct Inward Dialing (DID) numbers across more than 50 countries and
            all 50 US states. You can establish a local presence nearly anywhere in the world in just a few clicks.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question">What is the average latency for international calls? <div class="faq-icon"><svg
                width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
              </svg></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">By utilizing our proprietary global edge network and optimized SIP trunking, our
            international latency is consistently under 150ms round-trip, resulting in completely imperceptible delays
            and zero-clipping audio quality.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question">Can I integrate this with our current CRM? <div class="faq-icon"><svg width="24"
                height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
              </svg></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">Absolutely. My Call Connect operates with an API-first methodology, offering seamless
            webhook and REST integrations into Salesforce, HubSpot, Zendesk, and over 100+ platforms effortlessly.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container container-sm">
      <div class="cta-box">
        <div class="cta-content">
          <span class="badge badge-light">Global Expansion</span>
          <h2>Virtual Phone Numbers</h2>
          <p>We supply high-quality DIDs across all 50 states, Canada, and premium international locations. Direct
            Inward Dialing empowers your VoIP communications with excellent clarity.</p>
          <p class="cta-desc hide-on-mobile">Establish a local presence anywhere globally. Bypass traditional telephone
            trees and route incoming calls and faxes directly to the right agent instantly.</p>
          <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-light">View Pricing Plans</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
